<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="145" type="typification">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="145">Typification.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="145">
China. Guangdong Province, Taishan City, Chuandao Town, Xiachuan Island, on a grassland, elev. ca. 50 m, 
<geoCoordinate degrees="21" direction="north" minutes="37" orientation="latitude" precision="15" seconds="36" value="21.626667">21°37'36&quot;N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate degrees="112" direction="east" minutes="34" orientation="longitude" precision="15" seconds="30" value="112.575">112°34'30&quot;E</geoCoordinate>
, 17 July 2017, H. Huang, Q.J. Huang &amp; X.R. Zhong (GDGM59314, holotype!).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
